* {{ill|Fushou Palace in Puxi|de|Fushou-Palast in Puxi|ja|浦西境福寿宮|zh|浦西境福寿宫}}  
  Located outside the south gate of {{ill|Fuzhou City|de|Fuzhou-Stadt|ja|福州市|zh|福州市}}, it is the best-preserved Manichaean palace building, enshrining Lin Deng who once aided in disaster relief in Fuzhou.

